==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pyrone
<hw>Py`rone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G. <ets>pyron</ets>,
an abbr. of <ets>pyrokoman</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Org. Chem.)</fld> <def>An
unsaturated cyclic compound, <chform>C5H4O2</chform>, of which two
varieties are known, ⟦alpha⟧ and ⟦gamma⟧. ⟦gamma⟧-pyrone is the parent
substance of several natural yellow dyestuffs.</def></p>

